title: AFCON 2025: Recalled Ndiaye takes Senegal past 10-man Mali into semifinals
subhed: Senegal overcame the Malian team 1-0 on Friday, in the quarterfinals of the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations, in Tangier, Morocco. As the first team to qualify for the final four, Senegal will face either Egypt or Côte d'Ivoire.
